# The browser SPA needs no environment file.
#
# The SPA (index.html / app.js / styles.css) is served by the orchestrator
# from its bundled static files at http://localhost:8090 — there is no
# separate client process and no per-client config. All runtime settings live
# in orchestrator/.env (see orchestrator/.env.example).
#
# The legacy client/serve.py standalone dev server (which read ASGARDEO_*,
# CLIENT_ID, CLIENT_PORT, etc.) is a pre-v4 leftover and is NOT part of the
# current architecture. Do not configure it for the demo.
